<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Deal Portfolio</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        :root {
            --asml-dark-blue: #0F238C;
            --asml-bright-blue: #1297E4;
            --asml-yellow: #EAE136;
            --asml-light-bg: #F0F4F8;
            --text-primary: #1A1A1A;
            --text-secondary: #5A6C7D;
            --border: #D1DCE5;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #F0F4F8 100%);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(0deg, transparent 24%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 25%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 26%, transparent 27%, transparent 74%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 75%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 76%, transparent 77%, transparent),
                linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 24%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 25%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 26%, transparent 27%, transparent 74%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 75%, rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.02) 76%, transparent 77%, transparent);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1560 0%, var(--asml-dark-blue) 50%, #1565C0 100%);
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.15);
        }
        
        header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--asml-yellow) 0%, var(--asml-bright-blue) 100%);
        }
        
        .header-content h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        .subtitle { font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); font-weight: 400; }
        
        .stats-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.08);
        }
        
        .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
        
        .stat {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .stat::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -0.5rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 50px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--asml-yellow);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--asml-dark-blue) 0%, var(--asml-bright-blue) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .filters-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 2rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.1);
        }
        
        .filters { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
        
        .filter-btn {
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .filter-btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--asml-dark-blue) 0%, var(--asml-bright-blue) 100%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .filter-btn:hover {
            border-color: var(--asml-bright-blue);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.15);
        }
        
        .filter-btn.active { border-color: var(--asml-dark-blue); color: white; }
        .filter-btn.active::before { opacity: 1; }
        .filter-btn span { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        
        .filter-btn .count {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.625rem;
            background: var(--asml-yellow);
            color: var(--asml-dark-blue);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .filter-btn.active .count { background: white; color: var(--asml-dark-blue); }
        
        .content { padding: 3rem 0 4rem; }
        
        .deals-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.75rem;
        }
        
        .deal-card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            display: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        
        .deal-card.clickable {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .deal-card.clickable:hover .deal-title {
            color: var(--asml-bright-blue);
        }
        
        .deal-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--asml-yellow) 0%, var(--asml-bright-blue) 100%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }
        
        .deal-card.visible {
            display: block !important;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .deal-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--asml-bright-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.12);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
        
        .deal-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
        
        .org-logo {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1.5rem;
            right: 1.5rem;
            height: 32px;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 120px;
            object-fit: contain;
            opacity: 0.85;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        .deal-card:hover .org-logo {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .org-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1.5rem;
            right: 1.5rem;
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
            background: rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.08);
            color: var(--asml-dark-blue);
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.6875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            opacity: 0.75;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        .deal-card:hover .org-badge {
            opacity: 1;
            background: rgba(15, 35, 140, 0.12);
        }
        
        .deal-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            padding-right: 130px;
            color: var(--asml-dark-blue);
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        
        .deal-title .external-icon {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.6;
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        
        .deal-card.clickable:hover .external-icon {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .deal-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .deal-amount {
            font-size: 1.375rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--asml-dark-blue) 0%, var(--asml-bright-blue) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .deal-badge {
            padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
            background: var(--asml-yellow);
            color: var(--asml-dark-blue);
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        
        .deal-year { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 600; }
        
        .deal-location {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .deal-location .separator { color: var(--asml-bright-blue); font-weight: 300; }
        .deal-description { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.7; }
        
        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1560 0%, var(--asml-dark-blue) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 2.5rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        footer::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--asml-yellow) 0%, var(--asml-bright-blue) 100%);
        }
        
        footer p { font-size: 0.9375rem; opacity: 0.95; }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header-content h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
            .deals-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .filter-btn { padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
            .deal-title { padding-right: 90px; font-size: 1.25rem; }
            .org-logo { height: 28px; max-width: 100px; }
            .org-badge { font-size: 0.625rem; padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <script>
        // Filter functionality
        const filterBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn');
        const dealCards = document.querySelectorAll('.deal-card');

        filterBtns.forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const filter = btn.dataset.filter;
                
                filterBtns.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
                btn.classList.add('active');
                
                dealCards.forEach(card => {
                    const categories = card.dataset.category.split(' ');
                    
                    if (filter === 'all') {
                        card.classList.add('visible');
                    } else {
                        if (categories.includes(filter)) {
                            card.classList.add('visible');
                        } else {
                            card.classList.remove('visible');
                        }
                    }
                });
                
                // Update stats dynamically
                updateStats(filter);
            });
        });
        
        // Function to update stats based on visible cards
        function updateStats(filter) {
            let visibleCards = [];
            
            dealCards.forEach(card => {
                if (card.classList.contains('visible')) {
                    visibleCards.push(card);
                }
            });
            
            // Count transactions
            const transactionCount = visibleCards.length;
            
            // Calculate total deal value
            let totalValue = 0;
            visibleCards.forEach(card => {
                const amountElement = card.querySelector('.deal-amount');
                if (amountElement) {
                    const amountText = amountElement.textContent.replace(/[$M,]/g, '');
                    const amount = parseFloat(amountText);
                    if (!isNaN(amount)) {
                        totalValue += amount;
                    }
                }
            });
            
            // Count unique countries
            const countries = new Set();
            visibleCards.forEach(card => {
                const locationElement = card.querySelector('.deal-location');
                if (locationElement) {
                    const locationText = locationElement.textContent;
                    // Extract country (after the | separator)
                    const parts = locationText.split('|');
                    if (parts.length > 1) {
                        const country = parts[1].trim();
                        countries.add(country);
                    }
                }
            });
            
            const countryCount = countries.size;
            
            // Update the DOM
            const statValues = document.querySelectorAll('.stat-value');
            if (statValues.length >= 3) {
                statValues[0].textContent = transactionCount;
                statValues[1].textContent = `$${Math.round(totalValue)}M+`;
                statValues[2].textContent = countryCount + (countryCount === 1 ? '' : '+');
            }
        }
        
        // Make clickable cards open links in new tab
        dealCards.forEach(card => {
            if (card.classList.contains('clickable')) {
                card.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                    const url = card.dataset.url;
                    if (url) {
                        window.open(url, '_blank');
                    }
                });
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
